; Name ..........: CloseDroid4X
; Description ...: Forces Droid4X processes to close, and watches processes and services to make sure it has stopped
; Syntax ........: CloseDroid4X()
; Parameters ....: None
; Return values .: @error = 1 if failure
; Author ........: cosote
